# Date & Time Pickers

## Required components

Always use shared pickers from `@/components/common/pickers`:

- `DateField` — single date (`YYYY-MM-DD`)
- `DateRangePicker` — from/to date range
- `TimeField` — single time in 24h format (`HH:mm`)

Admin screens may import from `@/components/admin` (thin wrappers with `adminColors.primary` accent).

## Never use

- `@react-native-community/datetimepicker` or other third-party pickers in screens
- Raw `TextInput` for date or time entry
- OS-native date/time dialogs

## Required UX

**Date pickers**

- Year: scrollable vertical list (`YearScrollPicker`)
- Month: left/right buttons **and** horizontal swipe (`MonthNavigator`)
- Day: calendar grid tap (`CalendarGrid`)
- Modal bottom sheet with Cancel / Done

**Time pickers (24h)**

- Hour: scrollable vertical list (`HourScrollPicker`, 00–23)
- Minutes: left/right buttons **and** horizontal swipe (`MinuteNavigator`)
- Modal bottom sheet with Cancel / Done

## Props & values

- Dates: ISO `YYYY-MM-DD` strings
- Times: `HH:mm` (24-hour)
- Support `minimumDate`, `maximumDate`, `minYear`, `maxYear` where relevant
- Admin accent: `accentColor={adminColors.primary}`; customer/officer use default navy

## Extending

Add new picker behavior inside `apps/unified-app/src/components/common/pickers/` — never duplicate picker UI in screens.
